o takes place at irregular intervals every two and 11 years, and at different levels of intensity, also alters the climatic balances. At such times there is excessive rainfall; subseq\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 u\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
ent years are then generally dry and arid.
