c moths had recently dropped in North America, and that this was perplexing in the light of the classical scenario.290 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 In short, the presence or absence of lichens has no effect on moths. Kettlewell's thinking that lichens were a part of the supposed evol\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
